There once was a young man named Dulfric Elchester.
Dulfric loved to adventure like no other. He was
fascinated by the lands the creatures that lived within.
One day, Dulfric wandered father than he ever had before.
He was so far from home, and his surroundings were
so unfamiliar, he began to worry.
Dulfric thought that perhaps he should call out
for help. But alas, his instincts told him not to.
After hours of aimless wandering, as scared as he
was, Dulfric found something he didn't even know
he was looking for: the most beautiful lake in the world.
Dulfric sat and admired the lake, the flora,
and the fauna, and he felt as though he was
Little did he know, the lake had been tainted.
There was a presence in the lake that had
begun to corrupt all of its surroundings.
As Dulfric began to relax into a calm, he was attacked!
At first, he only felt pain, but slowly began to focus
It was but a glowing orb -- it oozed a viscous
liquid with a pungent, monstrous odor.
The orb seemed to gaze directly into his soul,
almost like it was hungry just for him!
Dulfric, a gentle yet hardy lad, sprang into action.
He found it within self to take down that
which was corrupting the lake, and made it a safe place!
There were many people that, just like Dulfric,
found a natural attraction to the lake. But Dulfric
was the one that made it safe for them to settle near it.
Thus, Dulfric became the Hero of his Namesake,
Nobody yet knows the origins of the orb,
but we know now for certain that the lake is one
of the most calm and peaceful locales in the Nation,
and Dulfric made it possible for us to experience it.
